      "span_text": "In an attempt to gain insight into the mechanism of spontaneous unbinding and in the spirit of the distributed computing approach, we performed several (20) simulations 30 nsec long at 300 K for the wild type and the H(H58)A complexes by assigning different initial velocities (see Materials and Methods)."
